{"article_id":"7Pi8IOzqO51dbNRy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump has said","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he is `` fairly close '' to a bipartisan deal","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to protect young undocumented migrants","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"known as Dreamers .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Mr Trump told journalists at the White House","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that any agreement must include `` massive border security '' .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"The president said","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"funding for his proposed border wall on the US border with Mexico was not part of the pact .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Mr Trump spoke","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"a day after talks with top Democrats Nancy Pelosi and Chuck Schumer at the White House .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Only last week Mr Trump stunned fellow Republicans","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"by making a budget deal with the Democrats .","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"The Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"( Daca )","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"programme allows some 800,000 people to remain in the US ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"and provides temporary permits for work and study .","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"The Obama-era scheme was put in place","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"to protect so-called `` Dreamers ''","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"- migrants","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"who entered the US illegally as children -","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"from deportation .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Only last week Mr Trump announced","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"he would cancel the programme .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"he was giving Congress six months","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"to enact a replacement plan for Daca recipients .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Deal or No Deal","depth":3},{"id":27,"text":"- Anthony Zurcher , Washington","depth":3},{"id":28,"text":"Welcome to another episode of Deal or No Deal , White House edition .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Unlike the classic game show , however , Donald Trump appears to be playing against himself .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"In a series of tweets , the president denied","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"he had struck an immigration/border security agreement with Democratic congressional leaders ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"then effectively endorsed the same terms","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"they set out in a press release Wednesday night .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"When speaking to reporters ,","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"he even echoed Democratic justifications","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"for why undocumented immigrants","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"who entered the US as children","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"should be given normalised residency status .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"This comes as a shock to some of Trump 's diehard anti-immigration supporters ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"who view any Daca-like agreement as amnesty for law-breakers .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Congressional Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"who were working on their own deal with Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"are in a daze as well .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"There is the possibility","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that this could be a Nixon-in-China moment for the president ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"where only a man","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"who campaigned vociferously against undocumented immigrants","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"could agree to give legal residency to hundreds of thousands of them .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Unlike Nixon 's China diplomacy , however , Mr Trump will need congressional Republicans to go along with his deal .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Many voted against his earlier agreement","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"to raise the debt limit","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"and avoid a government shutdown .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Heading to Florida on Thursday morning","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"to view the damage from Hurricane Irma ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Mr Trump told journalists :","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"`` We 're working on a plan","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"subject to getting massive border control ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"we are working on a plan for Daca .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"People want to see that happen . ''","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"He added :","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"`` So we met last night with ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"as you know ,","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"with Schumer , Pelosi and a whole group","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"and I think","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"we 're fairly close","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"but we have to get massive border security . ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"The president said","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"the congressional Republican leadership was `` on board '' with the plan .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"`` The wall is going to be built , ''","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"`` It will be funded a little bit later . ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Democrats have repeatedly vowed to block any legislation","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"that includes funding for the border wall","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"- a key campaign pledge by Mr Trump .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"After arriving in Florida ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Mr Trump denied","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that he would back a path to citizenship for Dreamers .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"During the presidential campaign , in August 2015 , Mr Trump said in a TV interview","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"that Dreamers `` have to go '' .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"But on Thursday , he voiced support for the young immigrants in language","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"that echoed former President Barack Obama .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"`` Does anybody really want to throw out good , educated and accomplished young people","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"who have jobs ,","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"some","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"serving in the military ?","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"Really ! ''","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"Mr Trump tweeted .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Paul Ryan , the top Republican in Congress , said","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Mr Trump 's meeting with Democrats `` was a discussion not an agreement or a negotiation '' .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Ms Pelosi told reporters","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"no deal had been finalised with the president .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"But she added :","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"`` We had an agreement","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"to move forward in our view , with a Dream Act as the basis","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"for how we protect the Dreamers ,","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"and for further discussions on what provisions","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"relating to the border","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"might be","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"and an accompanying bill or whatever","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"as we go forward . ''","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"Democrats failed to get Daca on to the statute books during the Obama administration ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"so it would be a political coup to succeed in doing so","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"when Republicans control the White House and Congress .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Congressman Steve King of Iowa tweeted at the president","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"that ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"if the latest reports are true ,","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"`` Trump base is blown up , destroyed , irreparable , and disillusioned beyond repair .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"No promise is credible . ''","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"One of Mr Trump 's earliest backers , media commentator Ann Coulter , tweeted :","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"`` At this point , who DOES N'T want Trump impeached ? ''","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Breitbart , the website","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"run by Mr Trump 's former chief strategist Steve Bannon ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"ran the headline , `` Amnesty Don ''","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"and accused the president of `` a full-fledged cave '' .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Fox News host Sean Hannity tweeted","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"that `` weak Republicans have betrayed voters ''","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"and pushed Mr Trump `` into arms of political suicide '' .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"The Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"( Daca )","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"programme was created in 2012 by then-President Barack Obama","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"to shield children of undocumented immigrants from deportation .","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"It also provided work and study permits for those","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"it covered -","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"popularly known as `` Dreamers '' .","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"In order to qualify for Daca ,","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"applicants under the age of 30 were required to submit personal information to the Department of Homeland Security ,","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"including addresses and phone numbers .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"They had to pass an FBI background check ,","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"have a clean criminal background ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"and either be in school ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"recently graduated","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"or have been honourably discharged from the military .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"In exchange , the US government agreed to `` defer '' any action on their immigration status for a period of two years .","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"The majority of Dreamers are from Mexico and other Latin American countries .","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"The Department of Justice has said","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"no new Daca applications will be taken .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":162,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":148,"right":161,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":146,"right":147,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":144,"right":145,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":140,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":0,"right":139,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":139,"left":1,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":141,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":151,"right":160,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":150,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":149,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":155,"right":159,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":16,"right":154,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":20,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":17,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":156,"right":158,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":158,"left":23,"right":157,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"pur